{"tid":904123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北極熊數量不減反增？愛斯基摩人稱生命受北極熊威脅","createTime":"2018-11-16T05:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T07:00:24.000Z","uid":212399,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b288e2e885308ee53777ed4e9504fc6bf58fd80d","tid":904123,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:40:28.000Z","msg":"近年多份研究顯示全球變暖令北極熊數量大減，令人關注北極熊存亡，但北極原住民的說法卻與科學家有分歧。<br />\n最近加拿大一份報告引用多個愛斯基摩人團體遞交的文件，指出愛斯基摩人觀察到北極熊數量上升，對社區造成生命威脅，北極熊已經超出與人類共存的界線。今年7月，兩名愛斯基摩人受北極熊襲擊死亡。<br />\n研究人員解釋，氣候轉變令海冰融化，獵物大減，遂令北極熊屢屢入侵原住民社區，而北極熊數量並沒上升。一名北極熊研究員指出，若不重視氣候轉變，將衍生更多「問題北極熊」。<br />\n愛斯基摩人反駁指他們族人居住在該地區數千年，但聲音常被忽略，質疑西方科學霸權不重視原住民的經驗。一名愛斯基摩獵人表示：「我們的知識一直在改進，如果你依賴這環境生存，你當然會熟悉它的轉變。」<br />\n他舉例稱，科學家一向依賴航拍推算北極熊數量，但根據愛斯基摩獵人經驗，暴風及大霧環境下才是北極熊出沒之時，故愛斯基摩獵人跟科學家推算的北極熊數量不一樣，但他同意科學家指要關注氣候變化問題：「我們想安全地跟家人享受這片土地。」"},{"pid":"453999b9b370fe7794caa2a834990fb30ae17963","tid":904123,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4b3b4acd52840f069478230dcd7e4e0ce03902","tid":904123,"uid":174420,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"依家暖化撚改左名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9934b0058d683b1c65ad82b2bdd6cd8493784a0","tid":904123,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"453999b9b370fe7794caa2a834990fb30ae17963","tid":904123,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d11cba1f9f699c9db16265bf15ce26d170560cc","tid":904123,"uid":21398,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:48:59.000Z","msg":"唔好將依個消息通知鄰國<br />\n唔止北極熊，連愛斯基摩人都食埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571091e63d4e3ab08feb637489c9cd601196058e","tid":904123,"uid":39855,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"我諗唔係熊多，係唔夠野食，開始襲擊人。"},{"pid":"00388fe4694b69d7184ebc0d0abcac4c5c93ba2a","tid":904123,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:56:33.000Z","msg":"當動物食過人肉就會狩獵人類<br />\n因為人類徒手時攻低防低又慢<br />\n<br />\n但好難次次成功追殺食過人肉的熊"},{"pid":"cea92ab4019fa66d93417736cb2c207e91c1fa25","tid":904123,"uid":4575,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"全靠我唔用飲筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8b5d55f412ef2b5f049ca3936b33fdd6fe07ed","tid":904123,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:58:43.000Z","msg":"專家去食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb23baa49ef90390fcf75ef91c8b15b556026a0","tid":904123,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9934b0058d683b1c65ad82b2bdd6cd8493784a0","tid":904123,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"453999b9b370fe7794caa2a834990fb30ae17963","tid":904123,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8a42e5ef79ae5a78b1d90278f51b3f5ead6bd9","tid":904123,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:04:49.000Z","msg":"北極熊：搵個人出黎同我隻揪，贏得到就放你走！"},{"pid":"477a3f5b09c521ac2c50ec5cb878300b687384ea","tid":904123,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"571091e63d4e3ab08feb637489c9cd601196058e","tid